- What?

45:19.091 --> 45:22.552
- Tom Brokaw stands to read the news.
- The whole time?

45:22.803 --> 45:24.595
- Yeah.
- He does?

45:25.639 --> 45:29.142
- He's done it for about a year now.
- Really? I gotta watch the news more.

45:29.476 --> 45:32.562
