46:25.657 --> 46:27.200
Actually, I download them off the Net.

46:27.242 --> 46:32.371
- I use www. Hotgod.com.
- Really?

46:34.708 --> 46:37.835
No. No, I was kidding.

46:38.045 --> 46:40.755
- So, you do write your own sermons?
- Yeah.

46:41.006 --> 46:43.007
He writes beautiful sermons.

46:43.050 --> 46:47.720
Actually, I like to improvise.
Keeps everybody on their toes.

46:47.805 --> 46:51.849
I guess you can't do that
too much with the news.

46:51.892 --> 46:54.393
- What?
- Riff.

46:55.437 --> 46:56.938
No, not really.

47:05.823 --> 47:08.825
I bet the Middle East is lovely
this time of year.

47:09.409 --> 47:12.036
Well, not if you're Kurdish.

47:14.081 --> 47:15.748
