47:44.820 --> 47:49.490
- Thank you. You look beautiful.
- You do. You look amazing.

47:49.616 --> 47:53.703
- Thanks, men.
- There's something about you tonight.

47:53.996 --> 47:56.455
- An absence...
- The cell phone.

47:58.125 --> 48:00.293
