having to cut the night short.

50:25.272 --> 50:28.107
I totally understand.
When the beeper beeps...

50:28.942 --> 50:30.901
I'm just going to be packing.

50:30.944 --> 50:35.823
Would you like to come up
for a nightcap, keep me company?

50:39.369 --> 50:44.081
I'd love to, but I should leave you.
I mean, you're going to Baghdad.

50:44.124 --> 50:48.210
Yeah. Yeah, long flight, I know.
Well, okay.

50:48.336 --> 50:52.423
But when you get back,
we should definitely get together.

50:53.133 --> 50:56.469
- I would love to. It's a date.
- Okay.

50:58.346 --> 51:00.181
- Bye.
- Bye.

51:14.112 --> 51:15.112
Taxi!

51:21.286 --> 51:23.412
- Well, this is me.
- Okay.

51:23.497 --> 51:26.165
You wanna come up for a while?

51:26.291 --> 51:30.336
I'd love to, but I should get home.
I have an early conference call.

51:30.837 --> 51:33.172
Me, too. I gotta talk to the big guy.

51:35.467 --> 51:37.301
- Right.
- Calls early.

51:38.553 --> 51:41.680
- Rain check, though.
- Yeah, definitely.

51:42.766 --> 51:44.058
Goodnight.

51:46.269 --> 51:48.521
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight.

52:16.216 --> 52:18.008
- Hi.
- Hi.

52:20.428 --> 52:24.890
- What are you doing here?
- I don't know, what am I doing here?

52:43.577 --> 52:45.161
I haven't screamed that hard

52:45.245 --> 52:47.580
since the US hockey team
beat the Russians.

52:47.664 --> 52:52.543
Incredible. I wanted to do that
since you walked off that airplane.

52:52.627 --> 52:56.881
