I'd like to discuss with you.

54:35.480 --> 54:38.274
Do you want to know

54:38.358 --> 54:44.822
If everything glittering
will turn into the gold

54:45.156 --> 54:50.494
I see in your hair?
I feel it could be there

54:51.079 --> 54:55.374
Somehow tonight

54:58.044 --> 55:00.921
And do you want to find

55:01.006 --> 55:07.261
Something worth saving?
The change would do me right

55:07.721 --> 55:13.100
I've been just waiting
and hesitating

55:13.226 --> 55:15.102
With this heart

55:17.272 --> 55:17.772
Of mine

55:27.282 --> 55:29.366
You're still a mystery

55:29.743 --> 55:36.248
But there's something so easy
in how you're sweet to me

55:37.208 --> 55:42.212
I feel completed
Like it's something I needed

55:42.255 --> 55:44.590
For this heart

55:46.301 --> 55:46.801
Of mine

55:56.811 --> 56:01.482
There's always something so tragic

56:02.942 --> 56:07.446
About a hopeless romantic

56:24.047 --> 56:27.800
We have a Jake Schram here
for Anna Reilly. Yes?

56:28.927 --> 56:30.010
Okay.

56:31.179 --> 56:34.973
