so let's forget this name thing,

56:35.016 --> 56:38.936
you can just say, "Hey, Jake,"
and I'll say, "Hey, T-Bone."

56:40.730 --> 56:43.816
- That pass is good for one hour.
- Okay. Thank you.

56:44.984 --> 56:49.738
Wednesday night, you have a call
at 7:00 and dinner at 8:00.

56:49.823 --> 56:53.117
All right. I'll make the call,
but cancel the dinner. I have a class.

56:54.536 --> 56:56.745
He's late.

56:58.164 --> 57:01.875
Oh, my God.
Are you guys getting serious?

57:02.544 --> 57:05.337
- No, no, no.
- Yes, you are.

57:05.422 --> 57:07.798
- No, we're not.
- I saw it, I can tell!

57:07.841 --> 57:10.592
No, no... Oh, he's here!

57:11.845 --> 57:13.679
- Hey.
- Hi.

57:15.223 --> 57:18.934
Debbie, this is Jake. Jake, vice versa.

57:19.018 --> 57:20.978
- How you doing?
- Hi, Jake.

57:21.020 --> 57:25.274
Can I just say... Good. Good for you.

57:25.358 --> 57:27.526
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

57:28.736 --> 57:32.406
- Debbie...
- Debbie... Debbie, what?

57:34.784 --> 57:36.577
The numbers are good for you, now?

57:37.078 --> 57:42.875
Good. Just run one more scenario
and assume an 8% I RR.

57:42.959 --> 57:44.418
Bye.

57:47.964 --> 57:50.883
- Hi.
- You're really gonna run an 8% I RR?

57:50.925 --> 57:54.595
- I'd go with 15%, at least.
