58:34.594 --> 58:38.305
- Ready? Let's go.
- Hang on, I'm learning something here.

58:39.015 --> 58:41.600
- We'll be late.
- You'll benefit from this.

58:43.019 --> 58:45.229
I can't Wednesday night,
I've a class.

58:45.271 --> 58:46.813
What class?

58:46.898 --> 58:50.359
I try new things.
