58:50.443 --> 58:53.654
Don't be embarrassed.
Many people take aikido.

58:53.738 --> 58:55.781
- Nope.
- Line-dancing.

58:55.823 --> 58:59.910
- Not even close.
- What's the big deal, why can't I know?

58:59.953 --> 59:02.037
- Feng shui?
- No!

59:02.413 --> 59:05.999
Don't be embarrassed if it is.
