01:04:14.934 --> 01:04:17.561
This is Brian, by the way.

01:04:18.187 --> 01:04:22.190
You know where to find me.
Call me, okay? Bye.

01:04:27.405 --> 01:04:30.156
- Gotta go now.
- Give me 20 minutes.

01:04:30.533 --> 01:04:34.077
- Twenty minutes? I'm late.
